name: MSRI-STATIC-JPG-PRSP-#01
description: v4w.enko - "MSRI-STATIC-JPG-PRSP-#01" is a perspectice projection jpeg static render of  3d Object, generated with custom definition. 4 lofts are rendered in 4 layers for each color:  Yellow, Green, Blue, Violet. The cells of the Red "3d voronoi" cube are linked to the attractor`s points of the lofts. Another one group of cells is linked to the same attractor points and are sitting as the White  cube .  The Perspective projection. Total 1 frame, 4200*4200px canvas. JPEG.
